Let $$\nabla$$ be a [[connection|Connection]] on the tangent bundle $$\T M$$ to a Riemannian manifold. We call the connection //metric// if for all $$X,Y$$ and $$Z$$ it satisfies

$$
X\langle Y,Z\rangle =
\langle \nabla_X Y,Z\rangle + \langle Y, \nabla_X Z\rangle.
$$